<section class="section ep5-process">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="ep5-process__heading">Simple, Relaxing, and Effective</h2>

    <div class="ep5-process__grid">

      <div class="ep5-process__step">
        <p class="ep5-process__step-title"><strong>Personalized Consultation</strong></p>
        <p class="ep5-process__step-desc">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses to review your wellness goals and confirm the right formula for your needs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ep5-process__step">
        <p class="ep5-process__step-title"><strong>Relax and Recharge</strong></p>
        <p class="ep5-process__step-desc">The IV drip is administered comfortably while you relax. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes from start to finish.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ep5-process__step">
        <p class="ep5-process__step-title"><strong>Feel the Benefits</strong></p>
        <p class="ep5-process__step-desc">Many clients report an immediate sense of mental clarity and a clean boost in energy after their session. Results continue to build over the following 24-48 hours.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ep5-process__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-lg);
    line-height: 1.3;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ep5-process__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ep5-process__step {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .ep5-process__step-title {
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ep5-process__step-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .ep5-process__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-inline: auto;
      text-align: left;
    }
  }
</style>
